Benchmark European coal dropped to
its lowest level in four days.  Thermal coal for delivery to Amsterdam, Rotterdam or
Antwerp with settlement next year fell 90 cents, or 0.7 percent,
to $129 a metric ton at 9:47 a.m. in  London , according to broker
prices compiled by Bloomberg. Thatâ€™s the lowest since Aug. 30.  Bloomberg tracks data from information supplied by ICAP
